Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无垠的时间停止心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人无声息地自燃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.22,0:00:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界异常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳里同学也...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与徒战斗是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二他...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要调整这个城市的扭曲似乎需要你的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛乔里小姐所说的“秘器”是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那“悼词诵读者”的助手是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 田中也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话该我说才是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你是“秘器”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是说真正的坂井悠二已经...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井悠二已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你很坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般无法这么平静地说出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很坚强 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直担心被大家知道后会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才也...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 得找到吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道了 关于我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此很受刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以得快点跟她解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解释也没什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实就是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“灵魂殿堂”差不多该进入最终阶段了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 教授
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火雾战士们完全没搞清楚那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看来那个并不是用来加剧扭曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲加剧可能是另一企图的副作用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 “追根究底”经常做无用功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:05:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这么无聊的事想让我干到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啓作和荣太还没到达玻璃坛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆教授的气息还是没察觉到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经驱使了这么多的燐子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来还有另外一个火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会和“追根究底”有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接问其本人更快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是 去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同于这些燐子的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是夏娜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新进来了一个 玛乔里小姐说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个东西的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙让吉田同学看清了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我也要快点到玻璃坛去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是火炬...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳里同学是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个城市所发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此也还是喜欢坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能一个人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是悼词诵读者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才战斗的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怪不得是蛮横的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 是老爷爷们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和疯教授无关啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你们也因没有“追根究底”的气息而心存疑虑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是用了什么手法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也对那...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是秘器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 表情很吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这么说你就是坂井悠二啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 居然是秘器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点伤害了那个小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把她牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她适合做我们的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这么个随便的理由就交给她这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然看到了那些 知道所受的冲击有多大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非要把她卷入这个圈子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于你来说 是个很重要的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学是个温柔的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该进入这个圈子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该一直待在我所无法返回的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 把你牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是动人场面 但首先应该关注现实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个自在式的实情已经略有眉目了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉田一美完全无关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是夏娜的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个自在式的作用在于
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用城市的扭曲 在空间中挖洞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空间中挖洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强行取走了一片拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说容易理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似懂非懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做那样的事有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 “追根究底”的所作所为一直都是莫名其妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 对城市有影响是毫无疑问的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上进行调律应该是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像昨天说明的那样协助我调律吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让吉田同学进一步牵扯进来的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置之不理的话 城市将更加乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学 我跟卡穆欣先生说好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我掉头就跑了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡迭什的心室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}卡迭什：埃及司爱情及美丽之神，也被视为母性的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 什么都没发生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看来有点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个自在式的影响下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布置在城市中的标记失去了反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思 无法调律？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐 能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 一言难尽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 玻璃坛启动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市上空的自在式的碗敞开着一个大口子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个城市都笼罩在自在式中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来那些都聚集到一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概在祭典主会场附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典主会场附近的河边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自在式的中心说是在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仓库那一带吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说起来“追根究底”有个助手 大部分身躯都是机械的燐子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“助人为乐的多米诺”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 失算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个家伙的话也就难怪无法察觉到气息了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁掉那个燐子的话 自在式也应该会被破坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 联络用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 马可西亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往常的话会说“一起去”...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“灵魂殿堂”的序言数值控制在了预想范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样领受的实验就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 顺便用我带来的试验版自在式进行先期实验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 火雾战士正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己想办法应付
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赶去集合点 通讯结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 一上来就火力全开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布下了弹开存在之力的防御性自在法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的进攻无效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始变形
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什么意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过刚才的设置很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险 难以出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于行动了 疯教授
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城市外面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没藏着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是没察觉到气息的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他想从哪里进入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在接近中这一点是毫无疑问的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}飞艇也会登场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“追根究底”就喜欢毫无意义的热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这次作战本身毫无意义也没什么奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地从空中来的话应该是有特殊意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说那里的空间像是被取走了一片拼图是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许那架飞艇是最后一片拼图...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小男孩的说法有一定道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个机器人来 还是快点去那个空间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正飞艇上肯定也有同样的设置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击了也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营造出那个空间的自在法也应该会对其有影响的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了靠近空间 就要解除设置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况危急的话我会发起攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不到悠二的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好远...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 变形结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 火雾战士们来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是高潮和最后一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自在法解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}班布里的街头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}骑上马儿去瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}无论去哪儿都随身伴奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么疯疯癫癫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让你为所欲为了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 妨碍我试验新作的纠缠不休的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们瞧瞧我的必杀绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是那么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没兴趣动手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才可说是结局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请避开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆利落地干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你要动手？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷要开炮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 吓跑了啊 大胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体了也没什么意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼啊疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有意义由我决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个到底是来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学这么温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法恢复了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的我已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学是人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是这么地温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身心都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢那样的坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 卡迭什的心室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你想象一下你的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那将正确调律这个城市的扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生后就一直生活着的这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温暖的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学是人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二不跟我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔赫米纳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吩咐你不要做过头了的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追根究底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务是做初步准备
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验本身是成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没理由教训我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 的确
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会顺利进展的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.92,0:24:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和十分想念的维尔赫米纳重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.52,0:24:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她敏感地察觉到了夏娜的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.76,0:24:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是她要夏娜做出一个决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.97,0:24:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无情的维尔赫米纳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
